STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Quameir T. WATERS, a/k/a Coo Coo, Quameier Waters, Defendant-Petitioner. C-673 September Term 2017
080211 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 9, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005382-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
